  "original_title": "\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8 , \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "India will continue to support efforts for stability and economic recovery - PM congratulates President Ranil",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi has said that as a close friend and neighbor of Sri Lanka, India will continue to support its efforts for stability and economic recovery.",
        "He mentioned this in his congratulatory letter to President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Prime Minister Narendra Modi has expressed hope that the term of office of President Ranil Wickremesinghe will fulfill the aspirations of all the citizens of Sri Lanka and foster economic stability.",
        "\"Congratulations on being elected as the 8th President of Sri Lanka. You have assumed responsibility at a very critical time in Sri Lanka.",
        "I hope that your tenure will fulfill the aspirations of all the citizens of Sri Lanka and nurture economic stability.",
        "As a close friend and neighbor of Sri Lanka, India will continue to support the Sri Lankan people's efforts for stability and economic recovery through institutions established under democratic means and constitutional framework.",
        "I look forward to working closely with you for the mutual benefit of the people of both countries and to further strengthen the ancient and close friendship between the two countries. I wish you a successful tenure.' It is mentioned that"
      ],
